&lt;p&gt;This should be enough to open the eyes of Muslims who blame the WEST for spreading HIV. The solution to HIV is not putting restrictions upon consenting adults, but to find a cure, or to take preventive measures. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For example, if scientists find a cure to HIV tomorrow, are then Muslims going to allow consenting adults to have sex without marriage? &lt;/p&gt;
