&lt;p&gt;Welcome to the world of Double Standards !!!&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Islamic Slavery has perpetrated abhorrent crimes against humanity. However, what is even more disheartening is the widespread ignorance surrounding these issues. Islamic preachers have cunningly concealed the atrocities from the general populace (including Muslims). If only people could become aware of these matters, the inherent compassion within us would triumph in this battle against Islam.&lt;/p&gt;
