&lt;p class=&quot;_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM&quot;&gt;And all other Ulama (of 4 Sunni Fiqh) during their time and after them and until now deny them on the issue of the nakedness of a slave woman. &lt;/p&gt;
