		<title> ٰIslamic Excuse: Slavery was not abolished due to ongoing Wars </title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://atheism-vs-islam.com/index.php/islamic-slavery/279-%D9%B0islamic-excuse-slavery-was-not-abolished-due-to-ongoing-wars"/>
