&lt;td&gt;Native Americans allowed to travel to Spain only on their own free will.&lt;sup id=&quot;cite_ref-33&quot; class=&quot;reference&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Timeline_of_abolition_of_slavery_and_serfdom#cite_note-33&quot;&gt;[33]&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
