&lt;td&gt;Queen Isabella bans the enslavement of&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indigenous_peoples_of_the_Americas&quot; title=&quot;Indigenous peoples of the Americas&quot;&gt;Native Americans&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;unless they are hostile or&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Human_cannibalism&quot; title=&quot;Human cannibalism&quot;&gt;cannibalistic&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;sup id=&quot;cite_ref-Sanchez_Galera_30-1&quot; class=&quot;reference&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Timeline_of_abolition_of_slavery_and_serfdom#cite_note-Sanchez_Galera-30&quot;&gt;[30]&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Native Americans are ruled to be subjects of the Crown.&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Christopher_Columbus&quot; title=&quot;Christopher Columbus&quot;&gt;Columbus&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;is preempted from selling Indian captives in&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Seville&quot; title=&quot;Seville&quot;&gt;Seville&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;and those already sold are tracked, purchased from their buyers and released.&lt;/td&gt;
