&lt;td&gt;Pope&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paul_III&quot; class=&quot;mw-redirect&quot; title=&quot;Paul III&quot;&gt;Paul III&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;forbids slavery of the&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indigenous_peoples_of_the_Americas&quot; title=&quot;Indigenous peoples of the Americas&quot;&gt;indigenous peoples of the Americas&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;and any other population to be discovered, establishing their right to freedom and property (&lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sublimis_Deus&quot; title=&quot;Sublimis Deus&quot;&gt;Sublimis Deus&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;sup id=&quot;cite_ref-35&quot; class=&quot;reference&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Timeline_of_abolition_of_slavery_and_serfdom#cite_note-35&quot;&gt;[35]&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
